Sinesis stepped up to Kitkat, he was a huge bot, Sinister not too far under
him.

"What are you talking about? Cashing checks your mouth can't write?" Sinesis
asked. He swung his claws around and took a chunk out of the wall of the
Predacon base. Sinister nodded to him.

"We have been asigned as the assassins, and you will be on our hitlist
before long, now, what we're you saying again?" Sinister said. Sinesis and
Sinister gave each other thumbs up and smiled, and then they walked back a
few feet and dropped into their chairs again.

"Our performance is spectacular!" Sinesis commented.

"None better than us!" Sinister said.

"Wanna join us?" Sinesis asked KitKat, holding up some dead animal and
taking a bite of it. Sinister laughs.

"You are awesome!" Sinister said.

"Yeah, I know!" Sinesis said. They smiled and poured themselves some wine.

"This stuff is supposed to have alchohol in it." Sinesis said.

"Yeah, it could impair your driving." Sinister said. They paused for a
while.

"Lets drink it!" Sinister said. They both drunk their glasses down and
stared a bit dumbfounded.

"That was weird!" Sinesis said. They both stared and started to drink the
entire bottle. Before long they were both asleep smiling...
